    "multicolumn_wcdj4N": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_VQTTyN": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Charts & Beyond",
            "text": "<p>Our digital test charts come with all the features you need to give an eye exam– accurately and comfortably. Not only do we provide the basics, but we also provide test customization. Use LEA symbols, pictures, numbers, tumbling E, LEA symbols, and much more. Truvision goes beyond a simple eye chart.<\/p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_PT7APG": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Full Setup for One Lane",
            "text": "<p>This digital acuity system provides a wireless keyboard and touchpad, Android tablet, 22” monitor, mounting hardware, HDMI and power cables, and a built-in manual for one-and-done calibration. This is everything you need for one lane of operation.<\/p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_wVj3hQ": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Simple Streamlining",
            "text": "<p>At Truvision, we believe that modern means efficiency. Your eye chart software connects to any WiFi-enabled device. This includes the keyboard you will receive; however, you can also operate the keyboard wirelessly. To make our software even more streamlined, our interface intuitively displays the patient’s view- without the need for remotes or clickers. Our ultimate goal is simplicity for both optometrists and patients.<\/p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "column_VQTTyN",
        "column_PT7APG",
        "column_wVj3hQ"
      ],
