        "review_1_txt": "<p><em>\"This system is so versatile, simple to use, and gone are the days when you have to worry about the patient \"memorizing the chart.\" I strongly recommend Truvision Visual Acuity system, and I have been very satisfied --- both with the product and the customer service\"<\/em><\/p>",
